ntent=\"Transform your outdated website into a modern, high-performance experience. Better UX, sharper visuals, and measurably improved results.\"/><link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/manifest.json\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Woods Websites | Custom Web Design &amp; Development\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Custom-built, high-performance websites crafted with care. Tailored to your goals, built to perform.\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://woodswebsites.com/images/logo/og-image.png\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Woods Websites | Custom Web Design &amp; Development\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Custom-built, high-performance websites crafted with care. Tailored to your goals, built to perform.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://woodswebsites.com/images/logo/og-image.png\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/images/logo/favicon.svg\" type=\"image/svg+xml\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/images/logo/favicon-32.png\" sizes=\"32x32\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/images/logo/favicon-16.png\" sizes=\"16x16\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/images/logo/apple-touch-icon.png\" sizes=\"180x180\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 transition-all duration-500\" style=\"opacity:1;pointer-events:auto;transform:translateY(0)\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-5\"><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-2\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold\" style=\"color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-0.04em\">WOODS WEBSITES<span style=\"color:var(--accent)\">.</span></span></a><nav class=\"hidden items-center gap-8 md:flex\"><a class=\"group relative font-sans text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors duration-300\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)\" href=\"/work\"><span class=\"transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-white\">Work</span><span class=\"absolute -bottom-0.5 left-0 h-px w-0 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:w-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span></a><a class=\"group relative font-sans text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors duration-300\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)\" href=\"/services\"><span class=\"transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-white\">Services</span><span class=\"absolute -bottom-0.5 left-0 h-px w-0 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:w-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span></a><a class=\"group relative font-sans text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors duration-300\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)\" href=\"/about\"><span class=\"transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-white\">About</span><span class=\"absolute -bottom-0.5 left-0 h-px w-0 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:w-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span></a><a class=\"rounded-full border px-5 py-2 font-sans text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text)] transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:!text-black\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" href=\"/contact\">Contact Us</a></nav><button class=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5 md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><span class=\"block h-px w-6 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"background:var(--text);transform:none\"></span><span class=\"block h-px w-6 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"background:var(--text);opacity:1\"></span><span class=\"block h-px w-6 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"background:var(--text);transform:none\"></span></button></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 md:hidden\" style=\"max-height:0;background:rgba(5,5,5,0.97);border-top:1px solid transparent\"><nav class=\"flex flex-col px-6 py-4\"><a class=\"border-b py-4 font-sans text-sm tracking-wide\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\" href=\"/work\">Work</a><a class=\"border-b py-4 font-sans text-sm tracking-wide\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\" href=\"/services\">Services</a><a class=\"border-b py-4 font-sans text-sm tracking-wide\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"mt-4 rounded-full py-3 text-center font-sans text-sm font-medium\" style=\"background:var(--accent);color:#050505\" href=\"/contact\">Contact Us</a></nav></div></header><div class=\"fixed bottom-4 right-4 sm:bottom-6 sm:right-6 md:bottom-8 md:right-8 z-50 transition-all duration-500\" style=\"opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transform:translateY(16px)\"><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"block rounded-full px-7 py-4 font-sans text-base font-semibold\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"background:var(--accent);color:#050505;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(46,196,182,0.35)\">Contact Us</a></div><main><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden pt-28 pb-14 sm:pt-36 sm:pb-20 md:pt-48 md:pb-28\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 50% 0%, rgba(46,196,182,0.05), transparent)\"></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6\" style=\"opacity:1;transform:none\"><p class=\"mb-4 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase\" style=\"color:var(--accent)\">Redesigns</p><h1 class=\"font-display text-4xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"color:var(--text)\">Your site,<!-- --> <span style=\"color:var(--accent)\">reimagined</span></h1><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl font-sans text-base leading-relaxed md:text-lg\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Breathe new life into an outdated website. Sharper visuals, better UX, and the performance your business deserves, without losing what makes you, you.</p></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pb-24\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><p class=\"mb-16 font-sans text-lg leading-relaxed md:text-xl max-w-2xl\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\">An outdated site costs you customers every day. We modernise your web presence from the ground up, preserving what works, fixing what doesn&#x27;t, and raising the bar on everything else.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-0\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"grid gap-6 border-t py-10 md:grid-cols-[220px_1fr]\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold tracking-tight\" style=\"color:var(--text)\">UX Audit</h3><p class=\"font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed md:text-base\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Before we redesign anything, we analyse how your current site performs. We identify friction points, drop-off areas, and missed opportunities so the new site fixes real problems.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"grid gap-6 border-t py-10 md:grid-cols-[220px_1fr]\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold tracking-tight\" style=\"color:var(--text)\">Visual Refresh</h3><p class=\"font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed md:text-base\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Updated typography, colour systems, and layouts that feel modern and on-brand. We don&#x27;t just make it look different, we make it look better and work harder.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"grid gap-6 border-t py-10 md:grid-cols-[220px_1fr]\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold tracking-tight\" style=\"color:var(--text)\">Content Migration</h3><p class=\"font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed md:text-base\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Moving to a new site shouldn&#x27;t mean losing your history. We migrate your existing content cleanly, preserving SEO value and ensuring nothing gets left behind.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"grid gap-6 border-t py-10 md:grid-cols-[220px_1fr]\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold tracking-tight\" style=\"color:var(--text)\">Speed Boost</h3><p class=\"font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed md:text-base\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Old sites accumulate bloat. We rebuild for performance from the start, stripping out the dead weight and optimising for fast, reliable load times on every device.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><p class=\"mt-14 border-t pt-14 font-sans text-base leading-relaxed md:text-lg max-w-2xl\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45)\">The end result is a site that looks and feels like it belongs to your business today, not five years ago. Faster, cleaner, and designed to keep pace with your growth.</p></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"font-display font-bold leading-none\" style=\"font-size:clamp(16rem, 35vw, 28rem);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.022);letter-spacing:-0.06em;opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\">01</span></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pb-24 md:pb-32\" style=\"padding-top:6rem\"><div class=\"mb-16 md:mb-20\"><p class=\"mb-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase\" style=\"color:var(--accent)\">Our Process</p><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl\" style=\"color:var(--text);max-width:640px\">We&#x27;ve got you covered<!-- --> <span style=\"color:var(--accent)\">every step of the way.</span></h2></div><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-start mb-14\"><div class=\"flex items-center flex-1 last:flex-none\"><button class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-3 flex-none focus:outline-none\" style=\"cursor:pointer\"><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-center rounded-full transition-all duration-500\" style=\"width:52px;height:52px;background:var(--accent);border:none;box-shadow:0 0 0 6px rgba(46,196,182,0.12), 0 0 24px rgba(46,196,182,0.35);transform:scale(1.08)\"><span class=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold tracking-wide\" style=\"color:#050505\">01</span></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase transition-colors duration-500\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9)\">Kickoff</span></button><div class=\"flex-1 h-px mx-4 mb-9 overflow-hidden rounded-full\" style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent);opacity:0.5;width:0%\"></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center flex-1 last:flex-none\"><button class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-3 flex-none focus:outline-none\" style=\"cursor:pointer\"><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-center rounded-full transition-all duration-500\" style=\"width:52px;height:52px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);box-shadow:none;transform:scale(1)\"><span class=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold tracking-wide\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.28)\">02</span></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase transition-colors duration-500\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.22)\">Design</span></button><div class=\"flex-1 h-px mx-4 mb-9 overflow-hidden rounded-full\" style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent);opacity:0.5;width:0%\"></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center flex-1 last:flex-none\"><button class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-3 flex-none focus:outl